## Backend Services (9 Lambdas)

| Service | Lambda | Purpose |
|---------|--------|---------|
| Auth | `auth_platform` | Telegram auth + JWT |
| Auth | `auth_jwt_authorizer` | JWT validation |
| User | `user_profile_mgmt` | Profile CRUD |
| User | `user_media_mgmt` | Media upload URLs |
| User | `user_media_processing` | S3-triggered image processing |
| User | `user_location_mgmt` | Location update/clear |
| Feed | `feed_query` | Nearby profiles |
| Chat | `chat_websocket_mgmt` | WebSocket connect/disconnect |
| Chat | `chat_websocket_msgs` | sendMessage, typingStatus, flashQueue |

## Data Model

- IDs: 8-character base64 strings (UUID v5)
- User (1) -> Profiles (1-3) -> Media (0-5 images) + Location History
- DynamoDB PK format: `ENTITY_TYPE#ID`, SK: `METADATA` or `ENTITY_TYPE#ID`

## Current State

- Backend: All core services deployed and functional
- Frontend: Auth, profiles, media, location, feed working with real APIs
- Chat/Inbox: UI done but using **mock data** — WebSocket integration pending
- Missing: Chat history REST API, match/block system, push notifications
